<p>
	Where is the future of technology going and what will happen to the startup industry in the next few years?
</p>
<p>
  With talks of a pending market crash and the uncertainty of the presidential election, it’s easy to think that the success for many early startups’ futures is going to disappear.
</p>
<p>
	But, with the continuous outpour of investments for early stage startups and large investments being made in VR, IoT, and other promising technologies, we wanted to get perspective from a seasoned venture capital professional, Sanjit Dang, investment director at Intel Capital.
</p>


